body: If Google publish a tensorflow iOS version is only want to prove that tensorflow **could** run under iOS, but not want to support iOS strategically, since iOS is from Apple, then it should clearly point out on the website that Only the published iOS example works on iOS, but not any other new user defined model, even for inception v1.
